comments: Oubre Jr. (CHA) initiates contact to Butler's (MIA) right shoulder while he is in his upward shooting motion and the contact affects his jump shot attempt.
Plumlee (CHA) establishes himself in Vincent's (MIA) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Lowry (MIA) briefly places an arm around Rozier (CHA) as he moves over the screen and the contact is marginal.
Lowry (MIA) pursues the rebound and marginal contact occurs with Plumlee (CHA).
Plumlee (CHA) absorbs the contact initiated by Butler (MIA) and maintains a vertical position while contesting Butler's shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) engages with Plumlee (CHA) as he is going to set the pick and the contact is marginal.
Vincent (MIA) and Plumlee (CHA) come together and marginal contact occurs as both players go for the loose ball.
Rozier (CHA) maintains a legal guarding position while contesting Butler's (MIA) shot attempt.
Vincent (MIA) reaches in upon Smith Jr. (CHA) receiving the pass and the contact is marginal.
Vincent (MIA) trails Smith Jr. (CHA) during his drive to the basket and the contact is marginal during his shot attempt.
Rozier (CHA) steps into Butler's (MIA) path and initiates the marginal contact during his drive towards the basket.  Butler does not dislodge Rozier from his defensive position.
Martin (MIA) maintains a legal guarding position while contesting Rozier's (CHA) shot attempt.
Butler (MIA) moves alongside Washington's (CHA) path and maintains a legal guarding position during his drive toward the rim.
Plumlee (CHA) does not maintain a legal vertical position while contesting Adebayo's (MIA) shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) reaches in and initiates contact to Rozier's (CHA) arm during his driving shot attempt.
Lowry (MIA) and Washington (CHA) come together and mutually engage and disengage during the screen attempt.
Washington (CHA) moves alongside Butler's (MIA) path and marginal contact occurs during Butler's shot attempt.
Strus (MIA) moves alongside Rozier's (CHA) path and maintains a legal guarding position while contesting the shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) and Plumlee (CHA) come together and marginal contact occurs during the rebound attempt.
Rozier (CHA) jumps for the rebound and incidental contact occurs with Strus (MIA).
Oubre Jr. (CHA) establishes his right foot as his pivot foot and lifts his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
McDaniels (CHA) attempts to commit a take foul against Vincent (MIA), but the contact is marginal.
Rozier (CHA) commits a take foul on Vincent (MIA).
Butler (MIA) maintains a legal guarding position while contesting Rozier's (CHA) jump shot attempt.  Any marginal contact is initiated by Rozier.
Washington (CHA) commits a take foul against Vincent (MIA).
